data.description: Florida living at its best!!!  You will love this wonderful pool home in Bentley Oaks.  Take a look at this gorgeous LVP flooring which is so easy to maintain!  Once you enter this great home, you'll notice the two guest bedrooms on the left and on the right you have a bonus room, which could be used as a study, workout room, playroom, etc.   Continuing on, you'll see the open living/formal dining areas, which offers the perfect layout for entertaining.  For extra entertaining room, open the french doors to the 12' x 30' screened patio, with three outdoor fans and two exit doors. Your great kitchen offers beautiful plantation shutters, an informal dining area, lots of counter space, cabinetry and a good sized pantry.  For the chef, there's a   double oven (2021),  super quiet dishwasher (2019), plus a wonderful 3 door refrigerator!  The main bedroom suite overlooks the back patio and pool area, with the main bath offering dual vanities plus storage underneath, a shower only and a large walk-in closet.  Outside you can enjoy the open pool deck, relaxing inground pool (new liner 2022) with a cute dolphin fountain.  WAIT, there's more....you've got a 12' x 32' workshop with an overhead roll-up door, power and it also has three windows, two exit doors.  At the roll-up door, there is a drive-up, and you can exit through the double gates out to the road, if needed.  The backyard is completely fenced and the yard is low maintenance.  More great benefits to you...solar panels (2017), solar pool heater (2016), solar water heater (2015), Rain Soft whole house water filtering system, including distilled water faucet in kitchen (2017), UV lighting system designed to eliminate mold in your AC unit and ductwork (2022), Pristine Air filtering system to prevent mold and allergens (2021), new roof (2022), HVAC (2018), new foyer LVP flooring (2023).  This home ready for you, so all you have to do is just move in!  What are you waiting for?   ,
